{{Quote|We Tanwas are just Tans with an extra syllable picked up during some civil war or other.|Captain Suz Tanwa's Hunt Log|<ref name="Wizards">{{Wizards|url=default.asp?x=starwars/article/sw20040819yavin5|series=Yavin: The Big Red One|text=Part 5: Twenty-Two Catch}}</ref>}}
The '''Tanwa Clan''' was a [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] clan on [[Rodia/Legends|Rodia]], directly descended from the [[Tan Clan]]. In the aftermath of an ancient civil war, the additional "wa" syllable was added.<ref name="Wizards" />

The most notable member of this clan was [[Suz Tanwa]], treasure hunter and archaeologist.<ref name="Wizards" />

